{"tid":368871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃毓民: 不淮恥笑任何政治監犯, 不論是左膠抑或是本土派","createTime":"2017-08-22T00:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T14:05:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":469,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a69aa180ad4fa21522018c92fc8043723bcdfd6e","tid":368871,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"黃毓民: 漢賊不兩立. 不淮恥笑任何政治監犯. 不論是左膠抑或是本土派.  而家唔係立場分歧問題, 是不同陣營也受政治迫害.  雙學在雨革可能曾經做錯誤決定, 但佢地而家的確受政府迫害.    而且客觀上, 黃之鋒等雙學三子最受國際支持, 是不能否認.<br />\n<br />\n我會出錢出力支持旺角行動被捕者, 但未能出錢支持左膠示威者, 因為我自己都唔夠錢, 而且左膠有自己的方法. 但我會全力聲援左膠政治監犯, 任何人恥笑和抹黑佢地, 我一定會還擊.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/D80Ol9nN3lU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD80Ol9nN3lU&d=Yugg0IjEz993OydPS6WIcHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=920c7687\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/D80Ol9nN3lU</a>"},{"pid":"92870f9ceb10b7c0b3a1d6afd80caaa81d82fd5b","tid":368871,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:48:50.000Z","msg":"都啱嘅"},{"pid":"1711ffb3cfc6ba73d1a0e3b06f7b098eaaa79c58","tid":368871,"uid":8748,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔學吓嘢啦 淨係識落井下石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc248bb84776bc9b0a15993dbae28e1474ee2e16","tid":368871,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1212d6f58981b148714f250fb4f6558b1bf3896b","tid":368871,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:50:37.000Z","msg":"毓民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ce9f27c0d1c6b8bb4a851a0566c71dc2c8f2d0","tid":368871,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bcd2cc314ba9077b85c9f0f74961